      <title>欧洲股市因阿斯麦和西门子前景看好而反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/european-stocks-edge-higher-before-macro-data-siemens-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西门子股份公司和阿斯麦控股公司的乐观前景帮助市场收复了唐纳德·特朗普大选胜利造成的部分损失，欧洲股市出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/european-stocks-edge-higher-before-macro-data-siemens-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 08:24:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员消化利多美国数据和供应预警，油价波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-14</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价几乎没有变化，因为交易商将美国数据显示的全国汽油库存大幅下降与国际能源署预测的原油供应大幅过剩进行对比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-14</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 23:29:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市在反弹后出现“疲态”迹象：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在选举后出现疯狂上涨之后，股市失去动力，在买家出现疲劳迹象的情况下，市场呼吁投资者稍事休息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
